* /l/ ar ttedwal /ř/, zun d : '''aɣyul''' -> '''aɣyuř'''
* Ur ar ttnṭaqn /r/ iɣ illa ḍaṛt n uɣri: ''tadda'''r'''t'' -> ''tadd'''aa'''t''.

Lemmer tlla tiɣra mbeɛd /r/ ar t nttnṭaq, zun d : ar tnṭaqn /r/ n ''tamara''.
* /ll/ ar ittedwal /ǧ/, Amedya : '''yelli''' -> '''yeǧi'''.
* /lt/ ar ittedwal /č/, Amedya : '''weltma''' -> '''wečma'''.
